<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Login Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .otp-container {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border: 2px solid #2563eb;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 10px;
      color: #2563eb;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .otp-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .timer {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .security-notice {
      background-color: #fee2e2;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Your Login Code</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>You requested to sign in to your Boilerplate account. Use the code below to complete your login:</p>

    <div class="otp-container">
      <div class="otp-label">Your Login Code</div>
      <div class="otp-code">{{otpCode}}</div>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">Enter this code on the login page</p>
    </div>

    <div class="timer">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>‚è± Time Sensitive:</strong> This code will expire in <strong>{{expiryMinutes}} minutes</strong>. If the code expires, you'll need to request a new one.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="security-notice">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>üîí Security Notice:</strong> Never share this code with anyone. Boilerplate staff will never ask for your login code via email, phone, or any other method.</p>
    </div>

    <p>If you did not request this login code, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure.</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      Best regards,<br>
      <strong>The Boilerplate Team</strong>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    <p>For security reasons, this code can only be used once.</p>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Boilerplate. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>